Design:
Gnome Labatory

Theme:
Crazy Gnome told locals that he wanted to study the wildlife.
He had brought with him a a few dwarven youths to help him 
capture and experiment on the wildlife. 

NPC:
Three dwarven youths (6th level hunters), one crazy gnome 
(15th level necromancer), and a few animals (4th level).

Treasure:
Weapons and armour. The hunters have their pay with them. 
